102
00:10:21,710 --> 00:10:25,330
Yuan!

103
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:26,920
Give me the document. Thanks.

104
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:36,420
All right, ladies and gentlemen,

105
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:37,670
