274
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:32,710
I'll bring you inside.

275
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:33,670
Come on.

276
00:17:34,170 --> 00:17:34,920
Let's go.

277
00:17:37,710 --> 00:17:39,540
